<span id="freeTextContainer6865744381655505494">The 500 hats of bartholomew cubbins was written by Dr.seuss. In the first bartholomew cubbin don’t have 500 hats, they have only one hat which belongs to father’s father’s father oldest hat in the kingdom of Didd. The kingdom of Didd Is on a top of a mountain and ruled by king derwin .Far off in the canberry bog, stood the hut of the cubbins family in the down of the mountain. The view to upside made the bartholomew cubbins small.one day bartholomew went to the market and came the king and all p</span>
  <span id="freeText6865744381655505494" style="display:none">The 500 hats of bartholomew cubbins was written by Dr.seuss. In the first bartholomew cubbin don’t have 500 hats, they have only one hat which belongs to father’s father’s father oldest hat in the kingdom of Didd. The kingdom of Didd Is on a top of a mountain and ruled by king derwin .Far off in the canberry bog, stood the hut of the cubbins family in the down of the mountain. The view to upside made the bartholomew cubbins small.one day bartholomew went to the market and came the king and all people took of their hat including bartholomew but king told bartholomew to take off his hat when he looked there was one more hat on his head then he take it off but there comes another hat in his heads so king told the royal coachman to took him to the palace very angrily. Then he took one more ….more… more 45 hats then 135 hats. Then came Sir snipps – maker of all hat for fine lords but he was not able to take off the hat a another new hat was coming there so the king called Nadd-Wise men, Father of nadd, Father of father of nadd but they also couldn’t do it then a small boy with a big lace collar came , Grand duke Wilfred – nephew of the king he taked a bow and arrow and tried it in bartholomew’s hat but it didn’t work a new hat appeared there on his head everytime . Then the king called yeoman of the bowmen but it didn’t work on his arrow he told that it was black magic so the king called the 7 magicians they came with each black cats and they chanted but it also didn’t work then king told exccutioner to kill the man , the exccutioner told that he will not kill a man with hat so I will took off your hat first he tried but it didn’t work so he was back at the king. It had been 453 hat which has taken off. Then Wilfred told that he will push bartholomew from the toppest turret ,king agreed. Each new hat was fancier than before.it was the 500th hat, which he was wearing now. But when he was upside, it was the beautiful hat in the kingdom of didd it has a ruby which was larger than any king had owned, it had ostrich plumes and cockatoo plumes, mocking bird plumes and paradise plumes. The king told that he will buy the hat in 500 pieces of gold, bartholomew agreed then he returned home with a bag of gold. </span>
